caption:"I entered crypto nine years ago, which means this is my third time watching everyone discover that markets go down. In 2018 the feeds went quiet and the tourists left. In 2022, same again. Both times, the tools everyone uses in the next cycle were built during the silence by the people who stayed. That is not motivation, it is just the pattern, and you can check it yourself. We are building hardware through this winter the same way we built through the last one, because when attention comes back it does not wait for you to start. If you are still here, you already know why. Say it in the comments for the ones who are wobbling.",
