script:"HOOK: My whole AI stack costs less than one intern. BUILD: An agent that codes and automates. A vault that holds everything I know. A connector that moves data between apps. A prospector that finds the right people. PAYOFF: Together they cover research, ops, outreach, and content prep, around the clock, no standups. Nobody got fired. The roles just never needed to exist. LOOP: The intern we did not hire? That budget ships product now.",
shots:["0-2s: price list b-roll, receipt printer sound","2-6s: screen recordings, one per tool, hard 1.5s cuts","6-9s: face cam, 'nobody got fired' held a beat","9-12s: product b-roll, budget line, loop text"],
